      • parseParamList

        public static List<Object> parseParamList(String context,
                          List<ParamDeclaration> paramDeclarations,
                          LinkedList<String> actualValues)
                                   throws ParseException
        Parses list of values, be it for option or for command.
        Parameters:
        context - information to pass to exception message, to be more user friendly
        paramDeclarations - the param declarations
        actualValues - values to parse against declarations; this list will be shortened according to paramDeclarations
        Returns:
        list of unmarshalled values
        Throws:
        ParseException - -
